{"tid":876553,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"隔離有堆第三者圍爐 有冇正印取暖區","createTime":"2018-10-25T16:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T03:23:09.000Z","uid":218556,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"365ab11260e89aa6157f04754690a7cbab05313f","tid":876553,"uid":218556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"一齊好多年 婚都定埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要一齊住緊<br />\n唔係我搬去佢屋企<br />\n係大家夾手夾腳租+打造新屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用左好多心機張羅d新嘅家電乜乜乜<br />\n住左一段算短時間<br />\n期間我做到好似佢老母咁搞d家頭細務<br />\n佢放工就坐喺度問食咩<br />\n明明我自己都有嘢要趕要做<br />\n<br />\n做女友做到好似老母咁<br />\n加埋工作壓力 久唔久會燥底 佢冇體諒<br />\n仲怪我成日比氣佢受 話我迫佢乜乜乜<br />\n然後一句話覺得同第三者開心d就乜撚都完<br />\n開你老母心，識得一個月唔知有冇緊係開心啦屌<br />\n仲要完全冇歉意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5c936b88ba157d51faa690aa6271f750cb2e53","tid":876553,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"冇女"},{"pid":"f214f8de2e3bea3278da4998e766feecdf78c169","tid":876553,"uid":218556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce5c936b88ba157d51faa690aa6271f750cb2e53","tid":876553,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"冇女"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n少樣嘢煩"},{"pid":"f5c1d0682f217c9bc1d64a9ee725d77724e30f18","tid":876553,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f214f8de2e3bea3278da4998e766feecdf78c169","tid":876553,"uid":218556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce5c936b88ba157d51faa690aa6271f750cb2e53","tid":876553,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"冇女"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:59:46.000Z","msg":"